4 SYNOPSIS:
5 This bill would require the Department of Human
6 Resources to request a waiver from the United States
7 Department of Agriculture Food and Nutrition Service to
8 exclude candy and soda from the definition of eligible
9 food for purposes of SNAP benefits.
10 If the waiver is granted, this bill would
11 require the department to prohibit the purchase of
12 candy and soda with SNAP benefits.
13 This bill would also require the department to
14 annually resubmit the request for a waiver if the
15 request is denied.
16
17
18 A BILL
19 TO BE ENTITLED
20 AN ACT
21
22 Relating to public assistance; to require the
23 Department of Human Resources to request a waiver to exclude
24 candy and soda from the definition of "eligible foods" for
25 purposes of SNAP benefits; to require the department to
26 prohibit the purchase of candy and soda with SNAP benefits if
27 the waiver is granted; and to provide for the resubmission of
28 the request, if the request is denied.
